title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-1.84 - Dry milk and dry milk products
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-1.84 - Dry milk and dry milk products

State Regulations

Dry milk and dry milk products, if used, must be reconstituted in the establishment. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10

comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
